'''Hilltop Emperor''' was a child's game. The goal of the game was to reach the top of a structure, becoming the "Emperor". In [[22 ABY/Legends|22 ABY]],<ref name="Date">The events of ''[[Survivor's Quest]]'' are dated to [[22 ABY/Legends|22 ABY]] by ''[[The Essential Reader's Companion]]''</ref> while aboard the ''[[Chaf Envoy]]'', [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Mara Jade Skywalker]] witnessed a version of the game being played in the background of a transmission from the [[Geroon Remnant]]'s vessel, with Mara noting the inclusion of a red headband that the winner would wave over their head in victory.<ref name="Survivor's Quest">''[[Survivor's Quest]]''</ref>

